genresAdvancedInfo.name: musica guerrerense
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Musica guerrerense is a traditional Mexican music genre that originated in the state of Guerrero. It is characterized by the use of brass instruments and percussion, with lyrics that often depict the struggles and triumphs of the people of Guerrero. The music is lively and energetic, with a strong emphasis on rhythm and dance.
